name: Planetary Defenses (V)
Lore: 'Key installations are protected from bombardment by a complex network of early-warning sensors, emergency shields and fast-response fighters.',
Text: 'Plays on any site. This location may not be targeted by Proton Bombs.  Death Star sites are immune to Expand The Empire.  Unless Death Star: Docking Bay 327 on table, Commence Primary Ignition is canceled.',
